  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "ch36-01",
      "text": "Avril a trouvé un mélange.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril stands at her workbench facing the viewer, carefully pouring one brass beaker into another as colorful liquids swirl together. The two beakers with their merging liquids are the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Oil lamps cast warm amber light, focused and experimental mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "mixing",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-02",
      "text": "C'est une émulsion.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "mixing",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-03",
      "text": "Le mélange qu'Avril a trouvé est bon.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mixing",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-04",
      "text": "L'émulsion reste dans le labo parce qu'il faut la planquer.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mixing",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-05",
      "text": "Avril regarde le mélange.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mixing",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-06",
      "text": "Il faut une insertion du mélange.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril faces the viewer holding a brass syringe, carefully inserting the emulsion into a small glass vial, a sparrow perched in a wire cage nearby. The brass syringe and vial in her steady hands are the focal point. Close-up, eye-level. Oil lamp light highlights the precise work, careful and meticulous mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "insertion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-07",
      "text": "Le moineau est là.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "insertion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-08",
      "text": "L'insertion est bonne si le moineau va mieux.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "insertion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-09",
      "text": "Le moineau regarde Avril qui travaille.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "insertion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-10",
      "text": "Il faut agir car le moineau attend.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "insertion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-11",
      "text": "13 jours de travail.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril sits at her workbench facing the viewer, exhausted but determined, a brass calendar on the wall behind her showing thirteen days crossed off. The row of failed experiment vials lined up on the bench is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Oil lamps glow warmly against the fatigue, persistent and weary mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "thirteen_days",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-12",
      "text": "Avril souhaite une chose.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "thirteen_days",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-13",
      "text": "Il y a 13 jours.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "thirteen_days",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-14",
      "text": "Elle souhaite trouver le mélange.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "thirteen_days",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-15",
      "text": "Le travail continue.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "thirteen_days",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-16",
      "text": "C'est agréable.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril faces the viewer holding a vial of glowing warm-colored emulsion at chest height, the sparrow chirping in its brass cage on the bench beside her. The softly glowing vial in her cupped hands is the focal point. Close-up, eye-level. The emulsion's pleasant glow mingles with oil lamp light, hopeful and satisfied mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "pleasant",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-17",
      "text": "On planque le sérum.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "pleasant",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-18",
      "text": "Le moineau est agréable.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "pleasant",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-19",
      "text": "On a planqué le mélange.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "pleasant",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-20",
      "text": "C'est agréable car le moineau va mieux.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "pleasant",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-21",
      "text": "Avril souhaite sauver le moineau.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril kneels beside the sparrow's cage facing the viewer, gently administering the glowing emulsion with a dropper, Darwin watching wide-eyed from the bench. The small sparrow receiving the serum is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Warm oil lamp light and the serum's glow bathe the scene, tender and life-giving mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "saving",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch36-22",
      "text": "Il faut planquer l'émulsion.",
